	   <tr><td colspan=2> For iksars go after jarsenth i think it is. If you are playing a iksar you might as well go after the wis items that ogre/troll/barb wouldnt wear since totemic looks better (looks matter more to me then a lil bit more wisdom) depending on your budget ill make a list of some items i think you might like.... (ill put a * next to things that are costly to your pocket) A lot of this is high end stuff.... <br>2 Plat jasper rings<br>1 Ivandyr's Hoop*<br>1 Forest loop<br>Chrysoberyl Talisman*<br>Platinum or Velium Ruby Veil<br>Iksar skull helm (no drop common in Lake of ill omen, just go loot it.. it decays a lot) <br>Chipped Bone bracer (dunno if iksars can wear)<br>Runed Mithril Bracer if you are a barb<br>Gatorscale leggings <br>Flayed Turmoilskin belt **(6k there about... go for Crystal belt if you cant afford this)<br>Bload stained tunic<br>Split paw hide gloves<br>Lizardscale Mantle<br>Molten cloak or mammoth hide *<br>1hb= Dark Ember *<br>Piercing= Jade chokodi prod *<br>Shield= Charred Gaurdian Shield (or Sarnak shield if you are REALLY rich)<br>Ranged Slot= Ebon war spear<br>Golden Efreeti boots if you can **<br><br>I think that about covers it. If you are iksar go for Jarsath i think its called.. if you are a barb/troll/ogre (ogre = best hehe) then go for totemic. Totemic stuff doesnt give much stats.. but AC is REALLY important, and it gives plenty of that. Not to mention being an ogre i look kinda like a big green bullfrog with full totemic. Well thats about it. Of course all this is assuming you are a twink. If not this would be a good equip list to go for (im still missing a few peices from this... like the 5k+ items like Flayed Turmoilskin belt, Golden Efreeti Boots, and Sarnak Shield.) <br><br>Please rate this post for better or worse<br>Nitsujlak Barshemguud Ogre Shammy of Prexus<br>"The good die young"<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
