	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok Since i am a Iksar Shaman i will tell you.<br>Try to get Enchanted Cabilis Scale Armor.&nbsp;&nbsp;That Armor should last to till your 30's or 40's when you start to get better armor.  If you have a Higher lvl try and get the Garou Bone Club or the Velium Etched Stone Mace.  Garou Bone CLub is very hard to get, i heard its harder then trying to get the Iksar Beserker Club.  And a CGS should do nicely as a shield or Testament of Vanear.<br><br>Try and work on your Piercing since the Epic is Piercing and don't be like me at 45 and have Piercing Skill of 7 LOL.  Jade Chokidai Prod is what i use and i love it although i almost never land a hit &lt;sigh&gt;.<br><br>Glodor Dimwit<br>&nbsp;<br>Patience is a Virture, and something i don't have</td></tr>
